{"tid":2292082,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE吸金力強　帶挈JYP事務所盈利逾1.6億","createTime":"2020-11-19T08:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T14:38:35.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c44b592e0b3101381ffa449a2cd250f7cc3a13f5","tid":2292082,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:28:54.000Z","msg":"台灣成員周子瑜所屬的人氣韓團TWICE活躍於日、韓，今年受疫情影響，未能照常開騷，但依然密密出碟吸金，單是2月至9月期間已推出了《MORE &amp; MORE》及《Fanfare》等5張日韓單曲及專輯，合共賣碟逾200萬張，加上於日、韓接拍飲品與護膚品等廣告，帶挈JYP事務所首3季銷售額高達7.2億港元，盈利佔1.66億港元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20201119/photo/bkn-20201119070024777-1119_00862_001_03p.jpg?20201119070323\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20201119%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20201119070024777-1119_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20201119070323&h=8cc57b64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n勁敵BLACK PINK今年推出《How You Like That》及《Ice Cream》等Hit曲，但處女專輯《THE ALBUM》上月才發售，雖然大賣過百萬張銷量，卻未有計算入首3季業績，所屬的YG事務所首3季盈利僅得140萬港元。而SM事務所今年單靠男團EXO成員先後推出solo碟，以及女團Red Velvet的小分隊「IRENE &amp; Seulgi」，疫情下收入大減，首3季赤字高達1.2億港元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20201119/photo/bkn-20201119070024777-1119_00862_001_02p.jpg?20201119070323\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20201119%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20201119070024777-1119_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20201119070323&h=0de01e43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fdcc971b817d2238db9fd6bf0b5ba0ad2237449","tid":2292082,"uid":224479,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"計左陪老闆食飯既profit未<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5feeae8724aa3db25632ae5f9079738e163049d6","tid":2292082,"uid":368098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:32:01.000Z",